data.description: Incredible House! Main floor has formal DR, LR w/FP, kitchen w/ extra island!Huge gathering room w/FP off Kitchen w large eat-in area*Lvl MBR w2 closets/2vanities/tub/tiled shower/*Upstairs has 4 bedrooms, oversized bonus and 3 bathrooms, one bedroom being 2nd master;
data.whatILove: The floor plan is absolutely awesome!    The kitchen is extra huge along with an oversized gathering room, oversized dining room and eat-in.    Two fireplaces on the main level, along with the master.  However, there's a 2nd master upstairs with its own bath, along with Jack-and-Jill bedrooms w/shared bath.  The 5th bedroom upstairs has a bath in the hallway.  To top it off, there's a huge bonus - 3 car garage long!!   If you have a big family, or need a big house, don't miss seeing this great home!
